curl -i <%= current_page.data.api_url %>/photos/1/comments
```

<!-- example response -->
<%= partial 'partials/responses/comments' %>

Returns a paginated array of all comments on the requested photo.

### HTTP Request

`GET <%= current_page.data.api_url %>/photos/:id/comments`

### Query Parameters

Parameter | Default | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
page      |         | specific page of results
per_page  | 30      | number of results per page


### Error Responses

Code | Message
---- | -------
404  | Couldn't find Photo with 'id'=